data.description: Rare offering, OutBaca Alpaca Farm invites you to experience the quintessential farm life. Spread across 25 picturesque acres, the majority of the land consists of meticulously maintained fenced-in fields, offering an ideal environment for raising Alpacas & Miniature Horses. This 1860 built, 6 bedroom 2 -1/2 baths farmhouse with 3 heating sources including 2 wood burning stoves to help heat home.  With updating and tender loving care you can bring this farm back to life!  Large 38x40 barn with loft for hay and stalls below for animals.    32x10 tool and machine shed.  Small un-insulated store attached to farmhouse with Summer Kitchen attached to back of home.   The back field is used for growing hay for animals.  Property spans across the road for even more fields and enclosed shed for animals.  Escape the hustle and bustle of city life and embrace a slower pace surrounded by a rural paradise. Whether you dream of expanding the alpaca or miniature horse herds, growing crops, or starting a hobby farm, this property offers endless possibilities.  Miniature horses, goats and Alpaca included in sale of property.   Do not let this opportunity slip by!  A Must See.
